Package edu.kit.joana.ifc.sdg.util.sdg

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SDGNodePredicate
    An SDGNodePredicate decides by some magic criterion, whether a given sdg node is 'interesting'.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultSDGNodePredicate
    Standard implementation of SDGNodePredicate.
    ReducedCFGBuilder
    Builds a reduced control-flow graph from a given SDG by removing 'uninteresting' nodes.
    ReducedCFGUtil
    Utility class for various methods operating on reduced CFGs.
